##==================================================================================================================================##
 #            ZFS is not like a traditional file system, ZFS is a separate system of its own that happens to handle files.          #
 #       You can think of it like in a standard system you have your system (Linux kernel) and this manages your file system.       #
 #                                      when you have a system with ZFS you have two systems                                        #
 #         The Linux kernel manages your system and ZFS thatmanages your devices and presents a filesystem to the Linux kernel.     #
 #                        Unlike regular file systems that work with files, ZFS works with blocks instead,                          #
 #           This provides enormous advantages and only your imagination sets the limit for what is possible to use ZFS for.        #
 #                                                                                                                                  #
 #                           ZFS will become an active friend in your system that will never let you down                           #
##==================================================================================================================================##


